    "description": "Join the Kale Consultants family as a Senior Software Engineer in Kanpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Kale Consultants:\nKale Consultants is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Rust\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kale Consultants!",
